{
  "stem": "27409.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Our job was to cut the supply lines of the Germans, to kill as many Germans, destroy the railway lines.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was our job.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We-- that happened in the forest near [NON-ENGLISH], a plane landed and brought the political commissar of the partisan movement in the Ukraine, the renowned leader Nikita Khrushchev to us.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I got a medal from him for distinction in my work in the partisan movement.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Other communists got even higher order, and officers rank It happened we fought all around in the region.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Korsun-Shevchenkivskyi was a bloodbath.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "All the German which were cut off, and the Russian army came nearer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we were met-- met the Red Army units.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we went with them to Vinnytsia-- liberated Vinnytsia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That was a main town of the region.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "From there, we got the order to go to the east, towards Nyester, to cut off the German troops which were fighting there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was von Manstein, I remember, the army group-- that was the commanding officer, General Manstein.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in '43.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And we, because we were going on my home town, so I wanted to be with the unit which was-- I knew the region.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was with-- together with the unit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In Vinnytsia, I met the first-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] let us call officer from the field bank.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I told them, I am also a trained bank clerk.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they told me-- gave me a paper-- when you come, when you are liberated, your town, you will be organizing the bank-- banking system in the newly liberated territory.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It took, in March-- 23rd of March, if-- if I remember well, we liberated my home town.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was with the first troop-- I entered the home town.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
